ElementDescription: Thinking back to when you started the study on [date started study], were there ever times between then and now when you took your antidepressant medication directly from the prescription bottle without first putting the pills in the electronic pill bottle we sent you?
Of all the times you took your antidepressant medication, how often was it from the electronic pill bottle?
Notes: 0 = Never or almost never; 1 = Rarely; 2 = Sometimes; 3 = Usually; 4 = Almost every time

ElementDescription: Now thinking back from when you started the study on [date started study], until your last interview on [date last interview], of all the times you took your antidepressant during this period, how often was it from the electronic pill bottle?
Notes: 0 = Never or almost never; 1 = Rarely; 2 = Sometimes; 3 = Usually; 4 = Almost every time; 5 = Every time

ElementDescription: Some people open the electronic pill bottle to see if it is working or for other reasons without taking the medication inside the bottle. Were there ever times when you opened the electronic pill bottle without taking your antidepressant medication?

Notes: 1 = A few days; 2 = Several days; 3 = Most days; 4 = All days or almost all days

ElementDescription: Now again thinking back to the period from when you started the study until your last interview, on how many days did you open the electronic pill bottle without taking your antidepressant medication?
Notes: 0 = Never; 1 = A few days; 2 = Several days; 3 = Most days; 4 = All days or almost all days
